title: Aftertop 200W Retractable Car Charger, 3-in-1 Independent Fast Charging, 2.3ft 105W Retractable Cable, Power Display USB C Car Charger for MacBook Pro, iPhone 16 15, Galaxy S25 S24 Ultra etc
description: Retractable USB C Car Charger: Built-in 2.3ft retractable USB C cable delivers 105W super charging, combined with 35W USB-C and 60W USB-A ports for 200W total power output, rapidly charging laptops, phones, tablets, or other devices simultaneously

top_reviews.title: Nice and fast
top_reviews.body: This is an excellent charger. I tested it out on my iPhone and it sure seemed to charge it faster than usual. It’s a significant upgrade to the one I had previously that just plugged into my car’s USB port. The charger itself seems to be solidly built and just snaps right into your cars power port. I like that it shows you the wattage while you’re using it even if I don’t understand much about those things in general. The cord stretches out plenty far and seems to be a nice rubber like material so I’m assuming it’ll be durable and work for years Read more
